#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.any.any:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`all`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.any.any:42 of
msgid "Test whether all elements along a given axis evaluate to True."
msgstr "测试沿给定轴的所有元素是否为 True。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.any.any:45 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.any.any:46 of
msgid ""
"Not a Number (NaN), positive infinity and negative infinity evaluate to "
"`True` because these are not equal to zero."
msgstr "非数字（NaN）、正无穷大和负无穷大都会被评估为 `True`，因为它们不等于零。"

